## ─── General (logs, patches) ───────────────────────────────
*.log*
*.diff
*.patch

## ─── Editor (VSCode) ──────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/*.code-snippets
!.vscode/cspell*

.history/

